Figure 2 shows that caravans on authorised private sites accounted for the largest proportion of the total number of caravans across England in July 2025 (62%). Caravans on unauthorised sites accounted for 16% of the total with caravans on authorised socially rented sites accounting for 22%. The underlying figures are included in accompanying Live Table 4.



